<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="sound-v">sound <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /saʊnd/    美 /saʊnd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(使) 发声；(使) 响：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>sound an alarm</strong> / a horn
鸣响警报/警笛</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The whistle sounded for the match.
比赛的哨声响了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>发...音：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The “s” in the “island” is not sounded. 
island中的字母s不发音。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>[用作系动词] 听起来；似乎：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Your adventure sounds exciting!
你的冒险经历听起来真刺激！</p><footer>译林② – 2</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>sound like:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>That sounds like a good idea.
那听起来是个好主意。</p><footer>2008 湖南</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="sound-as-if-though">sound as if / though</h3>
<p>1.<strong>听起来像：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It sounds as if you had a great time in London.
听起来你在伦敦玩得很开心。</p><footer>外研⑤ – 3</footer></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>— The movie starts at 8:30, and we can have a quick bite before we go.
— Sound great. See you at 8:10.  （2016 浙江改 改错）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. Sound改为Sounds  </p></div>